metadata.name: #1 Shibusawa Eiko dakimakura／渋沢栄子抱き枕
metadata.description:
資本主義の娘:渋沢栄子
Daughter of Capitalism: Shibusawa Eiko

渋沢栄子／女／14歳／資本主義の娘／
好きな事はお金を稼ぐことで大須の招き猫がモチーフ。
仮想通貨や電子マネーよりも現金が大好き。
元ネタはに日本の資本主義の父と言える渋沢栄一様。
Eiko Shibusawa / female / 14 years old / daughter of capitalism /.
Her favorite thing to do is to make money, and her motif is a beckoning cat in Osu.
She loves cash more than virtual currency or electronic money.
She is based on Eiichi Shibusawa, the father of capitalism in Japan.
